  "instructions": [
    "Heat olive oil in a large skillet over medium-high heat.",
    "Add chickpeas, soy sauce, salt, lime juice, and garlic. Stir well to combine.",
    "Reduce heat to medium and add allspice. Stir continuously for about 5 minutes until the mixture is fragrant and slightly thickened.",
    "Serve hot as a side dish or over rice.",
    "Store leftovers in an airtight container in the refrigerator for up to 3 days."
